PL Kyodan o e iglesia di maestro liberty ta un internashonal religion esei developed fo'i e zen budista kultura di japan tempran den e 20th century. pl teaches esei "life ta arte." humans tin been born na ekspresá nan propio unico individuality den tur kos nan hasi - "creating rason art". na asistí them den improving nan ta biba í overcoming hardships believers ta taught pakíko nan tin e problems í ta guided den solving them desde e patriarch (oshieoya-sama) í ministers. pl no kier tin un dibino buki (like un bible), ounke, nan tin pl 21 precepts í e pl 21 principles kuá were revealed desde e founders di e iglesia. 

pl twenty-one precepts: 

1. bida ta arte 2. man's bida ta un succession di self-expressions 3. homber ta un manifestation di dios 4. homber suffers si e homber fails na ekspresá mes 5. man's rason mes ta lost kuandu swayed desde sintimentu í emotions 6. man's rason mes ta revealed kuandu djé ego ta effaced 7. henter kosnan existí den mutual relationship na un otro 8. biba radiantly ban e solo 9. henter homber ta igual 10. strive pa creating mutual felididat 11. tin rason fe den dios 12. tin un kaminda (function) strabagante na kada "name" (existence) 13. tin un kaminda pa homber, í tin otro pa muhenan 14. henter ta pa mundu pas 15. henter ta un spil 16. henter kosnan mehorashon í develop 17. comprehend ta ki mas essential 18. na kada momentu homber stands na e crossroads di bon í evil 19. aktua kuandu bo intuition dictates 20. biba den un maestro unidat di mente í afèr 21. biba den maestro liberty

